From Monday, there will be two days of work on the Pacific Highway at Pimlico carry out landscape maintenance. Motorists can expect lane closures, traffic control and a reduced speed limit between 6am and 6pm.  

Also from Monday, there will be up to five nights and five days of work next to the Pacific Highway at Coolgardie to install signage. Motorists can expect traffic control and lane closures between 6pm and 6am and 7am and 5pm while the work is carried out.
